sound.

00:31:29.590 --> 00:31:33.250
And then we will start
discussing about new

00:31:33.250 --> 00:31:38.510
possibilities of how we recreate
those moments, the

00:31:38.510 --> 00:31:40.070
traditional lines.

00:31:40.070 --> 00:31:45.750
And then they will help me
to find out my ways.

00:31:45.750 --> 00:31:50.350
I will start to explore some of
my ideas on those passages

00:31:50.350 --> 00:31:52.450
