not certain rules.

00:32:00.450 --> 00:32:04.620
And so basically there are
a lot of alternatives.

00:32:04.620 --> 00:32:07.600
And the important thing is how
to organize the alternatives

00:32:07.600 --> 00:32:13.000
and how to balance them,
having a right pause.

00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:15.520
And this is the challenge
because you can do a lot of

00:32:15.520 --> 00:32:16.390
interpretations.

00:32:16.390 --> 00:32:19.940
But even it doesn't balance, if
it in the end doesn't make

00:32:19.940 --> 00:32:23.590
sense, then all those
feelings are wasted.

00:32:23.590 --> 00:32:27.290
And so first, you should
explore, and then you need to

00:32:27.290 --> 00:32:31.920
limit your interpretations
into certain ways.

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:35.980
And then in the concert, you
start everything new again,

00:32:35.980 --> 00:32:40.580
try to get inspired from the
actual stage and to recreate

00:32:40.580 --> 00:32:47.910
new feelings, new emotion, but
aware of the tradition lines,

00:32:47.910 --> 00:32:53.700
which will hold every
interpretation in the right

00:32:53.700 --> 00:32:55.710
speed and right pause.

00:32:55.710 --> 00:32:58.070
